<%@ page contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8" pageEncoding="UTF-8" %>
<%
    request.setAttribute("activeMenu", "arrivalNotice");
    request.setAttribute("activeGroup", "");
    request.setAttribute("activeSub", "");
%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="ctx-path" content="${pageContext.request.contextPath}">
  <title>TACS 도착통지서</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=block" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/resources/css/owner.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="app" id="app">
    <%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/owner/sidebar.jsp" %>
  <div class="main-wrap">
    <%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/common/header.jsp" %>

    <main class="content">
<div class="page active" id="pg-arrival-notice">
<div class="page-title-row">
<h2>도착통지서</h2>
</div>
<div class="alert-bar info" style="margin-bottom:16px">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">notifications_active</span>
          운송업체가 전달한 도착통지서(Arrival Notice)를 확인하고 수령 확인을 진행하세요.
        </div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px">
<div style="border:1px solid #e2e8f0;padding:16px 18px;background:#fff">
<div style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">미확인</div>
<div id="an-kpi-pending" style="font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:#dc2626">-</div>
<div style="font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:4px">수령 확인 필요</div>
</div>
<div style="border:1px solid #e2e8f0;padding:16px 18px;background:#fff">
<div style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">오늘 수신</div>
<div id="an-kpi-today" style="font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:#1d4ed8">-</div>
<div style="font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:4px">최근 도착통지서</div>
</div>
<div style="border:1px solid #e2e8f0;padding:16px 18px;background:#fff">
<div style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px">전체</div>
<div id="an-kpi-total" style="font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:#0f172a">-</div>
<div style="font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:4px">최근 30일 기준</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="two-col-wide" id="an-layout" style="display:block">
<div class="card-section" style="margin-bottom:0">
<div class="card-header" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px">
<h3>도착통지서 목록</h3>
<div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center">
<select id="an-status-filter" onchange="renderArrivalNoticeList()" style="font-size:12px;padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0">
<option value="all">전체</option>
<option value="pending">미확인</option>
<option value="confirmed">확인완료</option>
</select>
<input id="an-search" oninput="renderArrivalNoticeList()" placeholder="의뢰번호 · B/L · 운송업체" style="font-size:12px;padding:8px 10px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;width:240px; outline:none;"/>
</div>
</div>
<table class="data-table" style="margin:0">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>의뢰번호</th>
<th>운송업체</th>
<th>B/L 번호</th>
<th>도착일</th>
<th>수신일</th>
<th>상태</th>
<th></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody id="an-list-tbody"></tbody>
</table>
<div style="padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid #f1f5f9;font-size:12px;color:#64748b">
              도착통지서 수신이 지연되면 운송업체에 재전송을 요청하세요.
            </div>
</div>
<div class="card-section" id="an-detail-section" style="margin-bottom:0; display:none">
<div class="card-header"><h3>도착통지서 상세</h3></div>
<div id="an-detail" style="padding:20px"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
    </main>

    <%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/common/ownerModals.jsp" %>
    <%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/common/footer.jsp" %>
  </div>
</div>

<%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/common/ownerScripts.jsp" %>

</body>
</html>
